Lets add more content where it is not needed. In the lower levels. On which honestly you out level those items in about 4 levels anyway and will not use them. Hence why the need to ever try and get them? They will become redundant in about a week. <br>
<br>
More proof that Mythic has its' head up their own butt. <br>
<br>
Course I hear now Mythic is hiring someone to take over the high end aspects of the game. So lets look at this company in the full out view. <br>
<br>
1&gt; They licensed a net engine. They have no clue about how the engine works, they cannot make any specific changes. <br>
<br>
2&gt; The devs have no function. They have some great ideas but no one knows how to implement them. <br>
<br>
3&gt; They are forced to hire someone outside the company to try and make these changes. Again because they have no clue, all this while they have a big clue on collecting your money. <br>
<br>
4&gt; Their proven track record with any of their other games, I think they have at least 5 Multiplayer online games, to which they promise everything, and never deliver. Just like they are doing here. <br>
<br>
Again, more stalling. This time I think their latest excuse that all the devs got hit by a flu bug. We could probably go to the building they work in and film &quot;Outbreak 2&quot;. Convenient. <br>
