<br>
Lybernia, sorry to tell you but the frustrations are worse.  Granted when you die your equipment stays with your body, but the exp loss is non-fundable.  At least in eq a rez could get you exp back.  In DAoC it's gone.  You log on for 3 hours or more exp at 40+, die once and all of it is gone.  Not fun in my opinion.<br>
<br>
The end game is just that, the end.  By time you've hit lvl 34 you have probably been in every zone, every dungeon, and every realm, at least I was.  So what does that leave?  Nothing, useless and buggy RvR.  Broken relics that STILL don't work.  Being killed in 1 hit by an archer.  The list goes on and on.<br>
<br>
You can not make a successful pvp game with levels.  I don't know how many times this dead horse needs to be beat, but it's the truth.  This game is not RvR it's LvL period.<br>
<br>
I don't have the patience like Ut does to type out a 2 page rant but you get the point <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Point I'm trying to make is the game seems great below 30, once you get over, 31-35 the level mill starts kicking in, 35+ the game is terrible and is completely numbing to play.<br>
<br>
I've stopped playing for almost a month already, I have friends that still play and their finally seeing what I saw back then.  I'm sure they'll be quitting soon as well.  The game is so far from finished that if they didn't release it for another 6 months I guarantee it still wouldn't be close to completion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessageRange?topicID=987.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessageRange?topicID=987.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessageRange?topicID=987.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessageRange?topicID=987.topic&start=81&stop=86>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessage?topicID=1011.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=987.topic&index=40><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/shellene/feb/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=987.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.threadControl?topicID=987.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=987.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replie